  "title": "Electrical Project Manager (M&E / ELV)",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Electrical Engineering industry</strong> is seeking an <strong>Electrical</strong> <strong>Project Manager </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Electrical Project Manager (M&amp;E / ELV)</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Islandwide (depends on project’s location)</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5.5 days (Mon to Fri, 9am to 6pm; Sat, 9am to 1pm)</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $8,200 + Bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan, schedule, and manage electrical and ELV projects to meet timelines, budgets, and client requirements.</li>\n  <li>Lead project execution, coordination, and supervision of site works.</li>\n  <li>Review and approve designs, drawings, material submissions, and progress claims.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with safety, quality, and regulatory standards.</li>\n  <li>Manage project budgets, cost control, and supplier/subcontractor performance.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with clients, consultants, and contractors to resolve technical or site issues.</li>\n  <li>Oversee testing, commissioning, and project handover with proper documentation.</li>\n  <li>Mentor and guide engineers and supervisors for effective project delivery.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least a Diploma in Electrical Engineering, Mechanical Engineering or related discipline.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 5 years of relevant experiencein M&amp;E or electrical construction projects.</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of Electrical and ELV systems, project management, and site coordination.</li>\n  <li>Familiar with local codes, standards, and safety regulations.</li>\n  <li>Able to work in different site locationsand adapt to dynamic project environments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
